Package: BSSRed
Type: Package
Title: Blinded Sample Size Reestimation For Event Driven Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christoph Anten
Maintainer: Christoph Anten <christoph-anten@hotmail.de>
Description: This Package provides methods for blinded sample size reestimation for event-driven data in a two group seting. The implementation follows the presented Method provided by T. Friede et al..
